replies.body:
Alpha Strike is like the pull-out method. Always a bit of a gamble, but still fun to attempt at NAILING the timing.  
At worst, you're pregnant/shutdown, at best, you got your rocks off baby-free/scored a 1v5 pentakill. Its unpredictability is the issue. Riot plz put a condom on us in the form of a hotfix. {{sticker:slayer-jinx-wink}}

EDIT: PS "I WAS IN ALPHAAAA!!!" is a pretty daaaaaank meeeeeme
